These are Puzzles for 3x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: indie, house, d&b, blues, hip-hop, folk
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, baccarat, fonseca, havana, alhambra, montecristo
The people have 6 different hobbies: hiking, singing, fishing, writing, filmmaking, rock-climbing
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the fonseca-smoker##1
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 6. the havana-smoker is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 8. the fan house is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the fan folk is on the left of the fan indie##1
10. the fan hip-hop is the baccarat-smoker##1
11. the fan folk is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
12. the fan folk is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the baccarat-smoker##2
13. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the fan d&b and the alhambra-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |     4      |    5     |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | blues | hip-hop  | folk  | indie | house  | d&b   |
| Cigar           | havana | baccarat | montecristo | alhambra        | fonseca    | chaman |
| Hobby     | fishing    | writing     | rock-climbing   | filmmaking       | hiking | singing       |

