The people have 6 different jobs:  teacher, writer, musician, accountant, software-developer, chef
6 different games are played: poker, go, bridge, snooker, monopoly, whist
 1. the teacher is the person who growsiris##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is the software-developer##1
 3. the person who growsorchid is the person playing whist##1
 4. the accountant is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 5. the writer is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is between the teacher and the person playing monopoly##2
 8. the accountant is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 9. the chef is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
10. the person playing go is on the left of the writer##1
11. the musician is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
12. the person who growsiris is the person playing go##1
13. the person playing poker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |    5     |     6      |
| Flower      | iris     | daffodil | poppy     | orchid    | lily | begonia     |
| Job   | teacher | writer | accountant | chef | musician  | software-developer  |
| Game           | go    | bridge    | monopoly     | whist  | snooker    | poker |

