6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, rat, fish, mouse, ferret
There are 6 different favourite colors: brown, white, apricot, purple, blue, lavender
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 2. the person who likes blue is the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the cottage house is on the far left##1
 4. the cottage house is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 6. the person who likes white is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes brown is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the cottage house is the cottage house##1
10. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
11. the craftsman house is between the owner of the fish and the person who likes blue##2
12. the person who likes brown is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
13. the townhouse house is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
14. the townhouse house is on the right of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |   6   |
| House           | cottage  | cape-cod | craftsman     | tower | townhouse | art-deco |
| Pet   | mouse     | ferret      | goldfish | fish        | rat     | chinchilla |
| Color     | white | blue     | apricot   | brown          | purple      | lavender |

