 8. the person who likes ebony is the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person playing bridge is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
10. the person who likes turquise is the baccarat-smoker##1
11. the person who likes light-blue is between the person who likes green and the person who likes turquise##2
12. the person playing canasta is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |    4     |     5      |    6    |
