 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
10. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
12. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3      |     4      |     5     |    6    |
| Cigar           | ritmeester | tiparillo | alhambra | bongani | dunhill | swisher |
| Hobby   | video-games     | magic-tricks           | woodworking      | hiking        | drawing    | cooking  |
| Sport   | rugby | lacrosse     | ice-hockey  | surfing   | water-polo    | soccer |

