.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-18::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, fanta, almond-milk, juice, iced-tea
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, tulip, dahlia, sunflower, daffodil, orchid
There 6 different types of food: cranberry, onion, raspberry, radish, peach, apple
 1. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 3. the person eating cranberry is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 7. the person drinking juice is the person eating apple##1
 8. the person eating cranberry is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who growstulip##2
 9. the person eating onion is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating radish##1
11. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
12. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
13. the person drinking juice is the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |    5    |     6      |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | iced-tea | fanta   | water    | juice | 7up |
| Flower   | daffodil       | orchid   | tulip     | dahlia | sunflower   | balloon-flower      |
| Food   | raspberry   | cranberry | radish | onion  | apple | peach    |

