.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-19::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: scientific, documentary, action, superhero, fantasy, disaster
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: weightlifting, soccer, climbing, basketball, swimming, cycling
6 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, snake, hedgehog, bird
 1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 7. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the dog##2
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
10. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
11. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the snake##1
12. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
13. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
