The people have 6 different jobs:  manager, writer, photographer, dancer, architect, firefighter
House: cottage, modern, tower, farmhouse, victorian, gothic-revival
 1. the architect is on the far left##1
 2. the firefighter is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 3. the dancer is between the chaman-smoker and the siglo-smoker##2
 4. the farmhouse house is the manager##1
 5. the tower house is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 6. the oliveros-smoker is between the cottage house and the prince-smoker##2
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 8. the cottage house is the siglo-smoker##1
 9. the aristoff-smoker is the gothic-revival house##1
10. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the victorian house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
12. the firefighter is the fonseca-smoker##1
13. the tower house is the tower house##1
14. the writer is on the left of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |    5     |    6     |
